dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Oneida County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Oneida_Zoning_2014.gdb.[This polygon feature class represents the boundaries of zoning districts in Oneida County. This feature class is only an approximation on the zoning districts and is not intended to represent the legal zoning district boundary. See the Master Zoning District Document in the Oneida County Planning and Zoning office for zoning district boundary descriptions.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[Graphical representation.]
